data.description:
Lakeside of the Highway! Pool Home w/ amazing Lakeview! Welcome to this 3 Bed, 2 Bath, 3 Car Boat-Deep Pull-Through Garage & Large Casita. Enjoy your lakeview from the large front courtyard of this split floorplan home. The living area of the home features finished concrete floors, which lead you to an open kitchen w/ breakfast bar, natural gas stove, and tons of counter space.  The large master suite offers a private sliding door leading to the backyard. Master bath offers dual vanities, large walk-in shower w/ dual showers heads, and a large walk-in closet. The open floorplan provides ample space to invite your Family and Friends, and offers 2 spacious guest bedrooms. Tell your guests to bring their toys, and enjoy the large garage and plenty of space to park all the toys. Don't forget to enjoy the heated pool all year round! Pool and Jacuzzi are heated with natural gas, and new cool deck. Invite your guests to stay in the large Casita which is situated right by the pool but detached from main house which offers more privacy. The designer backyard offers mature fruit trees, artificial grass, palm trees, garden area, and shed. 
Don't miss out on this one!
